                     <interp inst="t18340703-210-defend1259" type="age" value="19"></interp>
                  </persName>
             was indicted for <rs id="t18340703-210-off1165" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18340703-210-off1165" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18340703-210-off1165" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18340703-210-cd1166" type="crimeDate">25th of June</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18340703-210-off1165 t18340703-210-cd1166"></join>, 1 handkerchief, value 2s. 6d., the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18340703-210-victim1260" type="victimName">
                        William 
                        Kirby
                     <interp inst="t18340703-210-victim1260" type="surname" value="Kirby"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18340703-210-victim1260" type="given" value="William"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18340703-210-victim1260" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t18340703-210-off1165 t18340703-210-victim1260"></join>
                     </persName>
                  , from his person
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>WILLIAM KIRBY. I am an <rs id="t18340703-210-viclabel1167" type="occupation">embosser</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18340703-210-victim1260 t18340703-210-viclabel1167"></join>. On the 25th of June I was in the <placeName id="t18340703-210-crimeloc1168">City-road</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18340703-210-crimeloc1168" type="placeName" value="City-road"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18340703-210-crimeloc1168" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18340703-210-off1165 t18340703-210-crimeloc1168"></join>, about eleven or twelve o'clock in the forenoon - I was looking into a shop window, and, on turning, I saw two young men by my side - I suspected them, and felt for my handkerchief - it was not in my pocket- I looked in my hat, and it was not there - I went on, and they were before me - when they came to James-street, one of them, who was the prisoner, ran off - I pursued, and cried, "Stop thief!" - I picked up my handkerchief in the track he ran - I pursued him to Old-street, and he was taken - there was no one but the prisoner and I in the street, when I picket up my handkerchief.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18340703-210-person1261">
                  THOMAS 
                  BILBOROUGH
               <interp inst="t18340703-210-person1261" type="surname" value="BILBOROUGH"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18340703-210-person1261" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18340703-210-person1261" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             (police-constable G 140). I took the prisoner - he said he got the handkerchief from another boy, but did not take it himself.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I was going along, and a boy came by in great speed - I stepped into the road - a gentleman pursued me - I said, "There goes the lad" - he would not go after him, but took me.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t18340703-210-verdict1169" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18340703-210-verdict1169" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs>. Aged 19. - <rs id="t18340703-210-punish1170" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18340703-210-punish1170" type="punishmentCategory" value="transport"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18340703-210-defend1259 t18340703-210-punish1170"></join>
